Today, on the National Day of Remembrance for Victims of Terrorism, we remember the Canadians whose lives were cut short or forever changed by a terrorist attack. Read my full statement:https://pm.gc.ca/eng/news/2019/06/23/statement-prime-minister-national-day-remembrance-victims-terrorism …

Aujourd'hui, en cette Journée nationale du souvenir des victimes du terrorisme, nous nous souvenons des Canadiens dont la vie a été volée ou changée à jamais par un attentat terroriste. Lisez ma déclaration :https://pm.gc.ca/fra/nouvelles/2019/06/23/declaration-du-premier-ministre-loccasion-de-la-journee-nationale-du-souvenir …

Today we remember the 329 innocent lives who were murdered June 23, 1985 on Air India Flight 182 because of a terrorist attack. Terrorism is a horrendous evil that we must continue to fight to ensure these heinous crimes are never repeated. My statement: https://www.facebook.com/AndrewScheerMP/posts/2738505356183199 …pic.twitter.com/YAFTZ4pHiF
